<div>
  <h1>You've Been Assigned a Gift Moment!</h1>
  <p>
    Hello {{name}},
  </p>
  <p>
    {{userFullName}} has just created a digital gifts capsule box for you.<br>
    The capsule <b>{{capsuleTitle}}</b> contains gifts, documents, and other digital memories.
  </p>
  <p>
    Stay tuned! You can sign in to your Gif Moments account using the button below:
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{signinUrl}}" style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #1976d2; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
      Sign In to Gift Moments
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>
    If you don’t have an account yet, you can register using the same link above.
  </p>
  <p>
    Capsule scheduled open date: <b>{{openDate}}</b>
  </p>
  <p>
    You will receive reminders a few days before the scheduled date so you don't miss it.
  </p>
  <p>
    If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <a href="{{signinUrl}}">{{signinUrl}}</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you,<br>
    The Gift Moments Team
  </p>
</div>